but we can try to escape

258
00:13:15,796 --> 00:13:18,565
while other people
are being targeted.

259
00:13:18,599 --> 00:13:23,571
after all,
gon can’t use nen right now,

260
00:13:23,604 --> 00:13:25,906
so i’ve gotta protect him,

261
00:13:25,939 --> 00:13:29,576
even if it means sacrificing
everything else.

262
00:13:30,677 --> 00:13:31,978
- ( Brush rustles )
- ( Gasps )

263
00:13:35,949 --> 00:13:37,584
( Animal bleats )

264
00:13:42,155 --> 00:13:44,591
Killua: Let’s hurry up.

265
00:13:44,625 --> 00:13:46,627
( Sirens blaring )

266
00:13:49,029 --> 00:13:50,998
( Tires screeching )

267
00:13:58,238 --> 00:14:00,107
Detective: Drop your weapon!

268
00:14:00,140 --> 00:14:01,942
Place your hands
behind your head,

269
00:14:01,975 --> 00:14:04,511
and get down on the ground!

270
00:14:04,545 --> 00:14:08,516
We’ll give you until the count
of three before we open fire.

271
00:14:08,549 --> 00:14:09,817
One...

272
00:14:09,850 --> 00:14:12,119
- ( Cheetu yawns )
- Detective: Two...

273
00:14:12,152 --> 00:14:13,520
Three!

274
00:14:13,554 --> 00:14:15,022
Cheetu: Ready.

275
00:14:15,055 --> 00:14:16,523
Detective: And fire!

276
00:14:17,758 --> 00:14:20,127
♪

277
00:14:24,965 --> 00:14:27,935
Officer: He disappeared.

278
00:14:27,968 --> 00:14:29,937
Aah! ( Screams )

279
00:14:29,970 --> 00:14:31,939
( Officers screaming )

280
00:14:40,180 --> 00:14:42,149
Cheetu: You’d think
they’d be faster.

281
00:14:42,182 --> 00:14:44,651
This is no fun.

282
00:14:46,286 --> 00:14:48,955
Newscaster: And in other news,

283
00:14:48,989 --> 00:14:52,025
at around noon today,
an unidentified creature

284
00:14:52,059 --> 00:14:54,929
killed seven people
in the suburbs of pata.

285
00:14:54,962 --> 00:14:56,964
it injured
multiple police officers

286
00:14:56,997 --> 00:14:58,699
that rushed to the scene

287
00:14:58,732 --> 00:15:01,435
before escaping
into the miera mountains.

288
00:15:01,468 --> 00:15:03,170
According to the authorities,

289
00:15:03,203 --> 00:15:06,773
the creature moved faster
than 200 kilometers per hour.

290
00:15:06,807 --> 00:15:08,275
It then said it would return

291
00:15:08,308 --> 00:15:10,944
and that they should
bring someone faster,

292
00:15:10,978 --> 00:15:15,583
which suggests it could be
a new species of magical beast.

293
00:15:15,616 --> 00:15:18,085
A mandatory evacuation order
is in effect...

294
00:15:18,118 --> 00:15:20,754
Killua: Pata city
and the miera mountains.

295
00:15:20,787 --> 00:15:22,856
Another city’s between us,

296
00:15:22,890 --> 00:15:25,693
with the miera mountains
on the opposite side.

297
00:15:25,726 --> 00:15:27,962
We should be okay.

298
00:15:27,995 --> 00:15:30,898
Newscaster: The government has
submitted a capture request

299
00:15:30,931 --> 00:15:32,699
with the hunter association.

300
00:15:32,733 --> 00:15:36,203
The association has accepted.

301
00:15:36,236 --> 00:15:38,004
- And now the weather.
- Gon: Hey, killua!

302
00:15:38,038 --> 00:15:39,006
- All done!
- Killua: Right.

303
00:15:39,039 --> 00:15:40,007
( Turns off TV )

304
00:15:40,040 --> 00:15:41,775
Gon: I guess tomorrow

305
00:15:41,808 --> 00:15:43,610
we’ll both be on our own, huh?

306
00:15:43,644 --> 00:15:46,147
killua: Yeah.
I’ll be training at the gym

307
00:15:46,180 --> 00:15:47,982
pretty much the whole day.

308
00:15:51,051 --> 00:15:53,620
Yeah, right.

309
00:15:53,654 --> 00:15:56,891
I can’t just leave gon alone
when he’s vulnerable.

310
00:16:01,528 --> 00:16:02,996
Palm: Gon, over here.

311
00:16:03,030 --> 00:16:04,031
Gon: Huh?

312
00:16:05,666 --> 00:16:07,668
♪

313
00:16:11,038 --> 00:16:12,606
Hmm?

314
00:16:12,639 --> 00:16:14,608
( Palm giggles )

315
00:16:15,676 --> 00:16:16,911
Gon: Huh?

316
00:16:16,944 --> 00:16:18,012
( Gasps )

317
00:16:18,045 --> 00:16:21,015
I didn’t even recognize you!

318
00:16:21,048 --> 00:16:23,350
Killua: Who are you?!

319
00:16:23,383 --> 00:16:25,619
Palm: Do I look strange to you?

320
00:16:25,652 --> 00:16:28,755
gon: Mm-mmm.
You look really pretty!

321
00:16:28,789 --> 00:16:32,293
Palm: Oh, no, please stop it.
You’re being far too loud.

322
00:16:32,326 --> 00:16:34,228
It’s just so embarrassing.

323
00:16:34,261 --> 00:16:37,131
gon: Huh?
I’m just telling the truth.

324
00:16:37,164 --> 00:16:39,099
( Palm giggles )
That’s enough.

325
00:16:39,132 --> 00:16:40,700
Come on. Let’s go.

326
00:16:40,734 --> 00:16:42,236
( Killua groans )

327
00:16:44,037 --> 00:16:46,306
♪

328
00:17:00,254 --> 00:17:02,189
Damn it!

329
00:17:02,222 --> 00:17:04,324
What the hell am I doing here?

330
00:17:04,358 --> 00:17:08,229
it’s like i’m
the creepy stalker or something.

331
00:17:08,262 --> 00:17:11,332
No. I can’t let it get to me.

332
00:17:11,365 --> 00:17:12,933
I have to protect gon.

333
00:17:12,966 --> 00:17:16,937
there’s no telling
when the enemy might show up.

334
00:17:26,380 --> 00:17:28,349
How far are they gonna go?

335
00:17:28,382 --> 00:17:30,384
♪

336
00:17:44,798 --> 00:17:47,167
( Gasps ) It’s here.

337
00:17:47,201 --> 00:17:50,905
It’s probably aura
from a soldier ant.

338
00:17:50,938 --> 00:17:54,975
It isn’t that close, but it’s
not that far away, either.

339
00:17:55,008 --> 00:17:58,245
There are faint traces
of aura here.

340
00:17:58,278 --> 00:18:00,347
Did it already pass through,

341
00:18:00,380 --> 00:18:03,383
or was it carried over
by the wind?

342
00:18:03,417 --> 00:18:06,987
either way,
i’ll probably run into it.

343
00:18:08,355 --> 00:18:09,990
Should I warn them?

344
00:18:11,325 --> 00:18:12,893
Gon: Well, this is it.

345
00:18:12,926 --> 00:18:14,861
Palm: What?

346
00:18:14,895 --> 00:18:15,896
Ah.

347
00:18:15,929 --> 00:18:17,931
♪

348
00:18:23,937 --> 00:18:25,972
It’s so pretty!

349
00:18:26,006 --> 00:18:27,307
Killua: No.

350
00:18:27,341 --> 00:18:31,412
If I told them now,
it wouldn’t help anyway.

351
00:18:31,445 --> 00:18:35,382
Besides, gon can’t use
his nen right now.

352
00:18:35,415 --> 00:18:38,818
If he gets all upset about kite
and flies off the handle,

353
00:18:38,852 --> 00:18:40,153
then he’s done for.

354
00:18:41,255 --> 00:18:43,324
And knowing palm,

355
00:18:43,357 --> 00:18:46,827
she’ll go 100% nuts
if I interrupt her date.

356
00:18:46,860 --> 00:18:49,463
If she breaks the silence
with her screaming,

357
00:18:49,496 --> 00:18:52,933
any ants that are nearby
will notice us for sure.

358
00:18:52,966 --> 00:18:54,835
Palm: Thanks, but i’m fine.

359
00:18:54,868 --> 00:18:56,169
( Giggles )

360
00:18:56,203 --> 00:18:57,438
( Gon chuckles )

361
00:18:57,471 --> 00:18:59,840
Killua: I can’t let them know.

362
00:19:02,109 --> 00:19:04,111
( No audible dialogue )

363
00:19:12,886 --> 00:19:15,455
I’ll handle this myself.

364
00:19:17,224 --> 00:19:19,226
♪

365
00:19:29,236 --> 00:19:31,271
( Gasps )

366
00:19:58,999 --> 00:20:03,337
rammot: Ah.
I thought I smelled a human.

367
00:20:03,370 --> 00:20:05,405
( Killua gasps )
It’s him.

368
00:20:07,140 --> 00:20:09,342
Rammot: I remember you.

369
00:20:09,376 --> 00:20:10,811
That’s right.

370
00:20:10,844 --> 00:20:13,080
You’re one of those brats
from before.

371
00:20:14,348 --> 00:20:17,184
It looks like your luck’s
run out, kid.

372
00:20:17,217 --> 00:20:19,920
You’re about to get
a taste of hell

373
00:20:19,953 --> 00:20:21,455
you’re never gonna forget.

374
00:20:21,488 --> 00:20:25,592
of course,
it won’t last forever, you know.

375
00:20:25,626 --> 00:20:29,864
Killua: I’ve led him upwind
far from the two of them.

376
00:20:29,897 --> 00:20:32,466
At least I could do that.

377
00:20:32,499 --> 00:20:34,134
Still...

378
00:20:34,168 --> 00:20:36,871
rammot: So where’s
that little friend of yours?

379
00:20:36,904 --> 00:20:39,340
Once you tell me his location,

380
00:20:39,373 --> 00:20:42,076
i promise you
that i’ll make it quick.

381
00:20:42,109 --> 00:20:45,879
Well, he can’t be that far.

382
00:20:45,913 --> 00:20:49,283
He is your friend, isn’t he?

383
00:20:50,551 --> 00:20:52,019
It doesn’t matter

384
00:20:52,052 --> 00:20:54,388
if you talk or not,
i suppose.

385
00:20:54,421 --> 00:20:57,124
I’ll just walk around
making lots of noise

386
00:20:57,157 --> 00:20:59,092
and swinging your severed head,

387
00:20:59,126 --> 00:21:03,030
and it won’t be long
before he comes to find me.

388
00:21:03,063 --> 00:21:05,499
That’s how humans are.
am I right?

389
00:21:05,532 --> 00:21:07,267
Killua: He’s right.

390
00:21:08,535 --> 00:21:10,971
I beat him right here and now,

391
00:21:11,004 --> 00:21:13,139
or it’s all over!

392
00:21:17,578 --> 00:21:21,982
I’ve gotta protect gon,
no matter what it takes.

393
00:21:25,152 --> 00:21:26,120
♪

394
00:21:26,153 --> 00:21:28,155
( Singing in Japanese )

